OL,3,C'It's coming home!': Excitement as
OL,4,CEngland prepare for World Cup 2026
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FEngland take on Argentina in the World
OL,8,FCup 2026 final on Wednesday evening -
OL,9,Fand excitement is certainly alive
OL,10,Facross Cumbria.
OL,12,FThe game kicks off at 8pm with pubs
OL,13,Facross the region showing the
OL,14,Fpenultimate match, and a dedicated fan
OL,15,Fzone set up at Carlisle United
OL,16,Ffootball club.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
