PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784299698
OL,3,C'It's coming home!': Excitement as
OL,4,CEngland prepare for World Cup 2026
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FSpeaking to people in Carlisle today,
OL,8,Fone man said: "I won't predict the
OL,9,Fscore, but I really really hope
OL,10,FEngland win, this could be a tough old
OL,11,Fmatch."
OL,13,FOne woman admitted: "Well the story
OL,14,Fis, I haven't watched any of the
OL,15,Fgames, so I feel like if I watch it,
OL,16,FI'll jinx it, so on behalf of the
OL,17,Fnation, I'm not going to watch it."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,328,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784299698
OL,3,C'It's coming home!': Excitement as
OL,4,CEngland prepare for World Cup 2026
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FAnother predicted a 3-1 score, with
OL,8,FEngland taking home the win: "Tough
OL,9,Fgame, but the pressure is on them,
OL,10,Fthey're former world champions, it's
OL,11,Ftheir title to lose."
OL,13,FBut, in Kendal, one family are
OL,14,Fdivided. For Tommy Sanchez this is the
OL,15,Fgame he hoped would not happen.
OL,17,FHe is from Argentina and played for
OL,18,FVelez Sarsfield but has lived just as
OL,19,Flong in the UK, after coming here to
OL,20,Fplay professional football for English
OL,21,Fteams, like Queen's Park Rangers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,328,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784299698
OL,3,C'It's coming home!': Excitement as
OL,4,CEngland prepare for World Cup 2026
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FHe now runs a cafe in Kendal,
OL,8,FWaterside Cafe, with his Argentinian
OL,9,Ffamily and they can't all agree who to
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Border, he said he
OL,13,Fwill be watching his former team mates
OL,14,FThiago Almada (Argentina) and Eberechi
OL,15,FOluchi Eze (England) playing in the
OL,16,Fsemi-final tonight but it is
OL,17,Fspectating he finds really
OL,18,Finteresting, saying Argentinian fans
OL,19,Fand the English fans are very similar,
OL,20,Fthough with a key difference.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,328,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784299698
OL,3,C'It's coming home!': Excitement as
OL,4,CEngland prepare for World Cup 2026
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FHe has this praise for anyone going to
OL,8,Fthe pub tonight, "When I moved to the
OL,9,FUK and all my friends used to go out
OL,10,Fto a pub to watch the matches, I was
OL,11,Flike, what is a pub? And I was like,
OL,12,Fthis is actually amazing.
OL,14,FLike a lot of people come together to
OL,15,Fwatch the matches and you get some
OL,16,Ffans and then the other team's fans in
OL,17,Fthe same pub chanting and supporting
OL,18,Ftheir teams, and it's actually
OL,19,Famazing."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,328,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784299698
OL,3,C'It's coming home!': Excitement as
OL,4,CEngland prepare for World Cup 2026
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FHe thinks it is going to be a tight
OL,8,Fmatch as England are "really strong"
OL,9,Fgoing into this game, but it is a
OL,10,Fmatch he dreaded as he does not know
OL,11,Fwho to support.
OL,13,F"So my family, because they only moved
OL,14,Fhere recently, they're still going
OL,15,Fwith Argentina. But for me, I moved
OL,16,Fhere, I played for English teams. I
OL,17,Fthink I'm half and half. I think I
OL,18,Fwill be happy with either result."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
