OL,3,C'It's coming home!': Excitement as
OL,4,CEngland prepare for World Cup 2026
OL,5,Csemi-final
OL,7,FAcross the region there will be plenty
OL,8,Fof support for the England squad and
OL,9,Ftwo local goalies in particular, Dean
OL,10,FHenderson from Whitehaven and James
OL,11,FTrafford from Cockermouth, who are
OL,12,Fboth included in Thomas Tuchel's 26-
OL,13,Fman squad.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/7
